        <num>CC 584</num>
        <heading>584.  Periodic charges</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 584.  Periodic charges
The usufructuary is bound to pay the periodic charges, such as property taxes, that may be imposed, during his enjoyment of the usufruct.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110775</p>
